{"tid":800401,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"作為一個利撚咁既分組賽真係得啖笑","createTime":"2018-08-31T00:03:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T07:19:43.000Z","uid":1734,"like":30,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d8dc55cb65adb2d6cb03d3dad8e6e2e7d9bcd583","tid":800401,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T00:03:31.000Z","msg":"講真咁同直接宣佈利記首名出線有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n真係令我地班利迷totally no mood to 捱夜睇波 嗱,我又分析下 首先PSG,唔好玩啦 法甲班霸，係法甲就龍歐聯就蟲，一次歐聯都無，咩尼馬麥巴比二線星，三分穩袋 <br />\n<br />\n拿玻里,,如果係皇馬就有少少可觀性，順便可以報上次歐聯ga仇)(不過算啦,遲啲決賽又見面) 我真係冇咩睇過依隊野..出半力夠贏，又三分 <br />\n<br />\n最後一隊,我連名都唔記得 我地出青年軍練下is ok,又3分<br />\n<br />\n加上我地利記4 大尖刀 ，怨婦沙拿，76文尼，傻鳩廢明奴，仲有賤種軒達臣 ，根本場場就一定大炒<br />\n<br />\n9分就一定..係睇下破唔破到歐聯史上最多入球紀錄，咁一面倒ga比賽,我冇興趣,大家決賽見<br />\n<br />\nP.S.比d咁ga對手利記....is侮辱..哈"},{"pid":"94504de743e7f9858c2311ecf4de2f9ce9f5a4e2","tid":800401,"uid":201731,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T01:02:01.000Z","msg":"悶啦"},{"pid":"d91c0a7e1331fc2f8146c23ac52dfde1d2f702f4","tid":800401,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94504de743e7f9858c2311ecf4de2f9ce9f5a4e2","tid":800401,"uid":201731,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T01:02:01.000Z","msg":"悶啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T01:09:26.000Z","msg":"咁年年都比咁既對手"},{"pid":"74e70c08f34b6efd4536e386b4b25166684d10aa","tid":800401,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T01:11:41.000Z","msg":"DKNY<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccfeebd783c365532f2e5fdca5915eecccdb7254","tid":800401,"uid":201731,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d91c0a7e1331fc2f8146c23ac52dfde1d2f702f4","tid":800401,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94504de743e7f9858c2311ecf4de2f9ce9f5a4e2","tid":800401,"uid":201731,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T01:02:01.000Z","msg":"悶啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T01:09:26.000Z","ms